WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 24=

01:42.467 --> 01:44.948
Your Highnesses,
what are you doing here?

01:45.068 --> 01:46.627
Waiting for you to open the shop.

01:48.028 --> 01:49.187
Please, come in.

01:55.907 --> 01:57.467
Look at this mess.

01:57.868 --> 01:59.267
Why are you living here?

01:59.747 --> 02:02.907
I worked on the accounts for too long
and simply stayed over.

02:03.467 --> 02:04.868
What brings you here so early?

02:05.627 --> 02:06.747
Is everything alright?

02:07.068 --> 02:09.507
All's well. I'm just here
to pick up something.

02:14.507 --> 02:15.388
Pick up something?

02:23.667 --> 02:24.868
Please get that for me.

02:32.028 --> 02:33.588
Alright. Let's go home.

02:36.067 --> 02:37.428
You never answered me.

02:37.828 --> 02:38.588
About what?

02:39.148 --> 02:41.667
The first time we met,
did you like me then?

02:42.507 --> 02:43.907
Didn't I already answer you?

02:46.108 --> 02:47.467
When did you answer?

02:47.467 --> 02:48.308
Just now.

02:48.308 --> 02:49.108
You didn't.

02:49.308 --> 02:50.428
I answered very clearly.

02:50.428 --> 02:52.308
I didn't have a runny nose, I tell you.

02:52.308 --> 02:54.067
- Would you believe me if I say I did?
- No.

02:54.067 --> 02:56.347
I say yes, you doubt.
I say nothing, you pout.

03:12.227 --> 03:16.028
Zuidie, you just recovered.
You should rest more.

03:16.268 --> 03:17.548
Don't overexert yourself.

03:18.067 --> 03:21.467
Ms. Wen, I'm fine.
I enjoy spending time with you.

03:22.268 --> 03:24.148
I'd like to walk around a bit later

03:24.347 --> 03:26.548
and pay my respects to His Highness.

03:27.388 --> 03:28.907
Alright, have a seat.

03:31.828 --> 03:36.787
Ms. Wen, I heard His Highness's marriage
was bestowed by the Empress Dowager.

03:37.187 --> 03:40.187
So he and his wife
didn't know each other beforehand?

03:41.467 --> 03:43.308
His Highness is slow to warm up.

03:43.467 --> 03:46.388
Getting along with Her Highness
must not come easily.

03:49.747 --> 03:52.507
They get along fine.

03:58.227 --> 03:59.467
If you want to look around,

03:59.467 --> 04:02.667
once we finish tea, I can take you
for a walk in the garden.

04:03.667 --> 04:04.467
Sure.

04:13.227 --> 04:15.388
Your Highness, perhaps I should do it?

04:20.427 --> 04:21.227
It's crooked.

04:22.867 --> 04:23.748
A little to the left.

04:25.547 --> 04:26.467
Now to the right.

04:29.268 --> 04:30.467
Still not right.

04:31.748 --> 04:32.547
No.

04:35.068 --> 04:36.588
Maybe a little more to the left.

04:37.748 --> 04:38.867
Are you playing me?

04:54.748 --> 04:57.588
Why did you suddenly decide
to hang the wind chime?

04:58.467 --> 05:01.467
Well, I brought it down
from Lishan Mountain.

05:02.628 --> 05:03.427
Come down now.

05:09.628 --> 05:11.227
Let go now. People can see us.

05:11.227 --> 05:14.427
I couldn't find you this morning.
Weren't you afraid I'd worry?

05:16.028 --> 05:17.467
I left you a note.

05:21.347 --> 05:22.467
Don't ever do that again.

05:39.347 --> 05:45.148
I accidentally found a wooden box
on your dressing table this morning.

05:47.787 --> 05:48.948
You touched my wooden box?

05:50.107 --> 05:52.508
I was indeed curious
and took a peek inside.

05:54.227 --> 05:55.427
But I didn't open any letters.

05:56.227 --> 05:58.907
They're your private letters.
I can't open them.

06:01.268 --> 06:03.107
It's fine. I'll show you.

06:45.987 --> 06:50.148
What are all these? Why did you send him
so many pieces of sheet music?

06:51.628 --> 06:54.828
He couldn't leave the mountain then.
I knew he loved the guqin deeply.

06:55.588 --> 06:59.748
So whenever I came across a new piece,
I'd just copy it and send it to him.

07:02.188 --> 07:05.347
Your bond surely runs deep.

07:06.828 --> 07:11.307
Yes. It's better than what you have
with that Lady Su.

07:14.268 --> 07:15.508
We were betrothed.

07:16.107 --> 07:20.107
But back then, we were both young
and barely met.

07:20.787 --> 07:23.427
Things changed later, and we lost touch.

07:26.667 --> 07:27.547
Why the sour face?

07:29.907 --> 07:30.907
I'm not sour.

07:35.907 --> 07:38.667
Mo Jingli probably isn't dead.

07:41.907 --> 07:44.427
I found a secret tunnel
inside Prince Li's mansion study.

07:44.667 --> 07:48.268
It leads through Dehua Ward, Ziyun Ward,
directly to the river outside the city.

07:48.307 --> 07:49.907
Afterward, I inquired with the boatmen.

07:49.987 --> 07:53.867
The night Mo Jingli had his 'accident,'
a boat was anchored by the riverbank

07:53.867 --> 07:55.107
and only left after midnight.

07:55.588 --> 07:58.828
It hadn't rained those days.
When I went there, I found traces.

08:03.188 --> 08:05.907
You're not surprised? You already knew?

08:08.148 --> 08:09.588
I'd guessed as much.

08:10.347 --> 08:13.547
Although a body was found
with matching wounds,

08:14.068 --> 08:16.948
the face was disfigured,
making it hard to confirm the identity.

08:17.427 --> 08:20.748
Moreover, after his 'accident,'
I made some inquiries.

08:20.948 --> 08:23.987
He has been plotting far and wide.

08:24.588 --> 08:27.427
He has placed his people
in the Six Ministries.

08:28.588 --> 08:32.108
Even a clandestine group
like Tianyi Pavilion had ties with him.

08:33.268 --> 08:36.628
Besides the assassination of Yuan Fang,
he's pulled other schemes.

08:37.787 --> 08:40.868
His ambition to reclaim
the Eastern Palace is now crystal clear.

08:41.508 --> 08:46.628
A person like him would never give in
if there was the slightest hope.

08:48.827 --> 08:52.508
It's Imperial Court of Judicial Review's
case now. I can't intervene directly.

08:59.148 --> 09:00.787
Are these all just music scores?

09:01.187 --> 09:02.427
What about these two?

09:04.028 --> 09:05.108
Not just music scores.

09:05.587 --> 09:07.108
Didn't you say you'd show me?

09:08.628 --> 09:09.468
I changed my mind.

09:09.468 --> 09:10.187
Show me.

09:10.388 --> 09:11.187
No.

09:11.388 --> 09:12.907
Why go back on your word?

09:13.067 --> 09:13.947
I'm not showing you.

09:13.947 --> 09:15.307
Don't make me get them myself.

09:31.508 --> 09:34.268
You usually take a nap around this time.

09:34.427 --> 09:35.587
What happened today?

09:36.148 --> 09:37.427
It's unbearably hot.

09:37.427 --> 09:40.547
These cicadas are so loud.
I can't sleep.

09:42.468 --> 09:45.947
Zuidie has been here for days,
and her health is clearly improving.

09:45.988 --> 09:49.067
She said she wanted to pay you a visit,
so I accompanied her here.

09:51.988 --> 09:56.067
Zuidie, didn't you say
you wanted to thank Yao and Li?

09:56.067 --> 09:57.947
You're here in front of them.
Why so quiet?

10:00.187 --> 10:03.148
I've been adrift like duckweed
for many years,

10:03.748 --> 10:06.707
never dreaming I'd return to my homeland

10:07.307 --> 10:11.348
to see you again,
Ms. Wen and Your Highness.

10:11.547 --> 10:14.388
That day, as I was out on errands,

10:15.307 --> 10:16.787
my old illness suddenly flared up.

10:17.947 --> 10:19.547
Luckily, I ran into Ms. Wen.

10:20.028 --> 10:20.868
Otherwise...

10:22.148 --> 10:25.067
It seemed even heaven
refused to take my life.

10:25.628 --> 10:28.547
I truly thank you, Ms. Wen.

10:29.547 --> 10:31.109
And thank you, Your Highness,

10:32.720 --> 10:33.787
for taking me in.

10:34.547 --> 10:37.547
Don't mention it.
Everyone needs help sometimes.

10:38.187 --> 10:41.067
You're Ms. Wen's old friend
and an acquaintance of mine too.

10:41.148 --> 10:44.187
Just staying a few days
doesn't call for such deep gratitude.

10:44.508 --> 10:45.307
Please sit.

10:46.388 --> 10:50.348
After all these years, Your Highness
has grown more courteous.

10:53.947 --> 10:55.868
Indeed, no need for such formalities.

10:56.108 --> 10:58.587
Why are you standing? Sit down quickly.

10:59.307 --> 11:00.108
Your Highness.

11:08.587 --> 11:10.907
It's too hot.
Have some icy sweets to cool off.

11:11.148 --> 11:13.028
Yes, it's truly scalding.

11:13.587 --> 11:17.187
This late in the year.
How come it's still this blistering?

11:26.108 --> 11:28.427
Back when I visited with Mom,

11:29.108 --> 11:32.108
Yao's mom was still here then.

11:32.827 --> 11:36.388
She also brought me a bowl of icy sweets
on that hot summer day.

11:36.827 --> 11:40.587
The chefs here were so skilled.
They'd carve designs onto the dishes.

11:40.827 --> 11:42.148
I loved butterflies,

11:42.748 --> 11:45.868
so she had them
cover mine in butterflies.

11:46.388 --> 11:48.868
They looked astonishingly lifelike.

11:49.348 --> 11:53.388
I hesitated to eat it,
clutching it tightly instead.

11:54.587 --> 11:57.988
But the tighter I held it,
the faster the ice melted.

11:58.707 --> 12:01.744
Until only a puddle remained.

12:03.792 --> 12:04.947
Nothing was kept.

12:06.587 --> 12:08.587
Now you're dwelling on the past again.

12:08.787 --> 12:10.947
The physician said
less brooding aids recovery.

12:10.947 --> 12:14.268
All this melancholy slows your healing.

12:17.028 --> 12:21.348
Thank you for your concern,
but truly, my health matters little.

12:21.868 --> 12:25.187
An early passing would reunite me
with my parents.

12:26.028 --> 12:27.388
You're talking nonsense.

12:31.868 --> 12:34.587
Passing beauty
stays a moment in the stream;

12:35.187 --> 12:38.307
people scatter like pieces
on a chessboard.

12:38.707 --> 12:41.628
Don't ask destiny
when our paths will cross;

12:42.307 --> 12:45.707
the clouds disperse
like silk blown by the breeze.

12:46.148 --> 12:49.667
Our meetings and partings are fated.

12:54.268 --> 12:57.628
Your Highness, the prefecture office
sent someone for you.

12:58.547 --> 13:00.368
Go attend your duties if you must.

13:03.056 --> 13:03.787
Business first.

13:04.228 --> 13:06.307
Yes, Xiuyao, go deal
with your official matters.

13:06.427 --> 13:07.748
We should leave as well.

13:43.988 --> 13:46.348
These cicadas scream relentlessly.

13:49.547 --> 13:52.868
Lady Su, I've been quite free
these past few days.

13:53.108 --> 13:57.947
So I had someone investigate a bit.
It turns out you still have relatives.

13:58.988 --> 14:04.268
After your family's exile, your brother
Su Huaizhong ended up in Huaizhou.

14:04.628 --> 14:07.907
Now he's a prominent
silk merchant there.

14:08.587 --> 14:11.148
Your younger sister married early
and escaped the exile.

14:12.468 --> 14:16.108
Her husband became
the prefect of Caizhou last year.

14:16.427 --> 14:19.108
He's well-regarded
and favored by his superiors.

14:19.787 --> 14:22.268
And your maternal uncles and aunts

14:22.388 --> 14:26.148
run teas shops in Jiangzhou,
prosperous from their tea business.

14:27.907 --> 14:29.348
What do you mean, Your Highness?

14:29.988 --> 14:31.067
I'm saying

14:31.587 --> 14:34.307
you're not alone and without family.

14:34.667 --> 14:38.468
If unwilling, you don't have to
serve as someone's maid.

14:39.388 --> 14:40.907
But I owe Princess Lingyun.

14:42.587 --> 14:46.148
I see. Then you should serve her
all the more faithfully.

14:51.187 --> 14:53.907
Ms. Wen, I've imposed too long.

14:54.427 --> 14:55.707
I'll take my leave now.

15:02.388 --> 15:03.907
Li, I...

15:04.508 --> 15:08.667
Ms. Wen, if she has other motives,
you won't be able to help her.

15:17.187 --> 15:18.148
Come see!

15:18.947 --> 15:20.388
One coin buys a full belly!

15:20.427 --> 15:22.348
Fresh-off-the-oven steamed cakes!

15:23.148 --> 15:24.348
New-style ones from Yangzhou!

15:25.108 --> 15:26.067
Look here!

15:26.348 --> 15:29.187
(You're not alone and without family.)

15:29.427 --> 15:33.228
(If unwilling, you don't have to
serve as someone's maid.)

15:35.827 --> 15:37.268
You're being unreasonable.

15:37.307 --> 15:39.587
Look at your cart.
It was already a wreck.

15:39.628 --> 15:41.628
It was fine until you broke it!

15:42.108 --> 15:43.067
Broke?

15:43.067 --> 15:45.988
Lady Su, this road's blocked.
We can't get through.

15:45.988 --> 15:47.707
You should've come the other way.

15:48.028 --> 15:49.187
Are you paying or not?

15:49.187 --> 15:49.868
Are you?

15:50.508 --> 15:52.228
Dream on! I owe you nothing!

15:53.628 --> 15:54.320
Move those in.

15:54.787 --> 15:55.307
Alright.

15:57.787 --> 16:00.187
It's alright. I'll simply walk back.

16:34.427 --> 16:36.628
You wretch, get lost!

16:49.232 --> 16:52.528
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

17:15.107 --> 17:16.188
Why won't you eat?

17:25.268 --> 17:27.387
Where is Qin Cang? Father, where is he?

17:27.387 --> 17:28.468
No more talk of Qin Cang.

17:33.067 --> 17:33.748
Tianyang,

17:35.067 --> 17:36.147
listen to me.

17:37.228 --> 17:40.387
I've arranged everything for you.

17:41.268 --> 17:42.867
You must leave the capital.

17:43.508 --> 17:45.948
Return to Lingnan. Go back to your mom.

17:49.948 --> 17:50.827
Tianyang,

17:52.988 --> 17:54.428
listen to me.

17:54.787 --> 17:55.908
Depart as soon as possible.

17:56.428 --> 17:57.787
By the time you return to Lingnan,

17:58.268 --> 18:00.508
it will be just the season
to enjoy pomelos.

18:01.627 --> 18:04.307
Weren't pomelos
your favorite as a child?

18:04.748 --> 18:06.387
You'll have fresh ones when you're back.

18:07.587 --> 18:09.547
Isn't he also your son?

18:11.508 --> 18:13.188
I heard Mom mention it.

18:14.028 --> 18:16.668
You and his mom grew up together.

18:18.067 --> 18:21.188
You kept him in an outer residence
against Mom's wishes.

18:21.668 --> 18:26.387
For years, every matter in the mansion,
big or small, was entrusted to him.

18:27.587 --> 18:28.787
I've always thought

18:30.468 --> 18:32.387
he was your most valued son.

18:34.028 --> 18:34.867
Father,

18:37.107 --> 18:39.468
if one day, I am in your way,

18:39.708 --> 18:41.347
would you also kill me?

18:50.988 --> 18:53.067
Pack your things and depart soon.

19:19.787 --> 19:23.708
(Tianyang said this thing
looks like a black gauze cap.)

19:23.908 --> 19:25.067
(To me,)

19:25.387 --> 19:29.347
(it looks more like a flowerpot,
perfect for planting flowers.)

19:36.547 --> 19:37.587
What's the matter?

19:37.587 --> 19:38.748
(Xiangqi Pavilion)
Open the door!

19:38.988 --> 19:41.948
Master Feng booked the whole place.
Come back another day.

19:42.948 --> 19:45.748
My apologies. Sorry about that.

19:47.988 --> 19:50.867
The one performing on stage
is Lady Yusheng.

19:51.188 --> 19:52.948
She is now the most popular dancer.

19:53.107 --> 19:54.347
She debuted just last year,

19:54.508 --> 19:57.188
and business at Xiangqi Pavilion
boomed instantly.

19:57.867 --> 20:02.107
Today I pulled some strings
to book the entire place privately.

20:02.988 --> 20:06.188
That's why we're lucky
to enjoy her graceful dance.

20:10.067 --> 20:12.387
Good posture and a solid stance.

20:12.668 --> 20:17.147
But she lets her gaze wander,
still lacking something.

20:18.547 --> 20:19.988
Yun, you're quite the expert.

20:23.228 --> 20:26.787
It seems you're a frequent visitor here.

20:27.748 --> 20:28.787
I rarely come.

20:33.147 --> 20:34.347
Only for occasional socials.

20:35.188 --> 20:36.708
I'm far too upright.

20:36.867 --> 20:39.988
I don't like debauched places
bustling with singsong girls.

20:40.988 --> 20:44.188
Then why haven't you married yet?

20:44.268 --> 20:46.307
Then why haven't you married yet?

20:47.067 --> 20:48.387
Do you have a beloved in Cangbei?

20:50.827 --> 20:51.627
No.

20:52.668 --> 20:53.468
I do.

20:56.948 --> 21:00.508
My beloved seems reluctant.

21:05.387 --> 21:09.748
Not exactly reluctant,
just always evasive.

21:13.948 --> 21:16.387
She's always evasive,
yet you're still into her?

21:16.508 --> 21:19.748
That evasiveness
refers to outward appearances.

21:23.708 --> 21:27.387
An evasive facade suggests
there might be something hidden within.

21:28.107 --> 21:32.387
Perhaps when you know what she's hiding,
you'll change your mind.

21:32.668 --> 21:33.468
I won't.

21:36.587 --> 21:38.547
Alright. You won't.

21:39.147 --> 21:39.948
Eat.

21:42.228 --> 21:43.508
Shrimp dumplings.

21:43.827 --> 21:46.867
Their shrimp dumplings
are considered unrivaled.

21:48.307 --> 21:50.787
I remembered you don't like ginger,
so I told them to skip it.

21:51.268 --> 21:52.107
Feel free to eat.

21:59.668 --> 22:01.228
What's that in your hand then?

22:02.387 --> 22:03.508
Something I carved for fun.

22:03.627 --> 22:05.908
The bone of an exorcism beast.
It tests fortune.

22:05.988 --> 22:06.787
How?

22:07.827 --> 22:08.827
It's very simple.

22:08.948 --> 22:11.147
You toss it up
and see which side lands face up.

22:11.627 --> 22:12.508
Let me test yours.

22:13.188 --> 22:13.988
Childish.

22:14.268 --> 22:15.268
Try it.

22:18.508 --> 22:19.468
You're a businessman.

22:19.468 --> 22:21.708
So we'll test
your financial fortune first.

22:22.468 --> 22:23.307
Blow on it.

22:28.784 --> 22:29.587
(Auspicious)

22:29.587 --> 22:30.387
Auspicious.

22:30.508 --> 22:33.228
Purple clouds come from the east.
A sign of flourishing wealth.

22:33.468 --> 22:34.908
It's simply unstoppable.

22:36.668 --> 22:38.908
Alright, I'll hold you to that.

22:39.748 --> 22:42.268
Now, let's test your marriage fortune.

22:45.627 --> 22:49.268
See if you can find a good match
on this trip to Dachu.

22:50.668 --> 22:51.387
Blow on it.

22:57.872 --> 22:58.988
(Auspicious)

22:58.988 --> 23:00.508
Auspicious again?

23:02.028 --> 23:03.708
Yun, your trip won't be in vain.

23:03.948 --> 23:06.668
It seems your destined partner is here.

23:08.347 --> 23:11.867
Then this third time,
let's test your safety.

23:19.371 --> 23:20.624
(Auspicious)

23:21.147 --> 23:22.147
Still auspicious!

23:22.627 --> 23:24.228
You have such immense luck.

23:24.228 --> 23:26.908
See how fortune chases after you?
You can't escape it.

23:27.120 --> 23:28.372
(Auspicious)

23:33.347 --> 23:35.627
Both sides are auspicious.
A double blessing.

23:36.627 --> 23:39.307
This means you
and this token share a fate.

23:39.428 --> 23:40.228
Take it as a gift.

23:42.387 --> 23:44.147
Alright. Thanks, Feng.

23:44.428 --> 23:45.748
Now. Let's drink.

23:51.728 --> 23:54.992
(Qingfeng Mingyue Tower)

24:18.708 --> 24:20.107
Why call me here so late?

24:20.867 --> 24:22.627
Help! Mo Lao'er!

24:23.468 --> 24:24.268
Master Feng,

24:24.547 --> 24:26.468
no food, but you're this drunk?

24:26.468 --> 24:28.188
What should I do?

24:29.228 --> 24:30.787
What do you mean?

24:32.827 --> 24:34.067
I'm done for.

24:35.067 --> 24:36.867
Your father has kicked you
out of the house?

24:38.188 --> 24:39.228
He would never.

24:39.748 --> 24:41.468
Qingfeng Mingyue Tower is closing?

24:43.508 --> 24:45.307
Could you wish for anything good for me?

24:45.468 --> 24:47.307
That sworn brother of yours
has abandoned you?

24:56.587 --> 24:57.787
You get me.

24:59.387 --> 25:00.508
Not that obvious, is it?

25:01.827 --> 25:04.468
Seriously? Master Feng, you...

25:07.787 --> 25:09.867
Adult matters aren't for you
to understand.

25:10.147 --> 25:10.827
Leave.

25:11.988 --> 25:13.428
I'll leave. Don't touch me.

25:13.428 --> 25:14.708
- Out.
- You're dangerous.

25:15.468 --> 25:16.787
Be careful, Your Highness.

25:20.508 --> 25:21.387
Exactly as I thought.

25:22.067 --> 25:23.708
Close correspondents meeting,

25:24.387 --> 25:27.228
long separated and reunited,
will cause trouble.

25:28.107 --> 25:29.867
You don't know the situation.

25:30.748 --> 25:32.107
The very first time I saw her,

25:32.908 --> 25:34.748
she was caked in mud from head to toe.

25:35.627 --> 25:38.468
So dark and skinny
that I thought she was a man.

25:39.508 --> 25:44.307
But how come
she seemed different this time?

25:45.107 --> 25:45.908
I see.

25:47.428 --> 25:48.787
Lust at first sight?

25:50.067 --> 25:51.587
You still don't get me.

25:52.908 --> 25:54.347
Does she know you're onto her?

25:58.748 --> 26:00.228
I don't think so.

26:00.867 --> 26:02.827
I've been very restrained.

26:03.748 --> 26:04.988
So what are you going to do?

26:05.067 --> 26:08.188
I'm simply confused.

26:09.387 --> 26:12.908
The first time I saw her,
she was disguised as a man.

26:14.107 --> 26:16.508
Given the circumstances,
it's understandable, right?

26:17.827 --> 26:21.708
Why did she disguise herself
as a man to meet me again?

26:24.948 --> 26:27.387
Could she be hiding
from revenge-seeking enemies?

26:29.748 --> 26:32.067
Or did she flee a forced marriage?

26:38.268 --> 26:40.668
I have no idea
whether she likes me or not.

26:40.988 --> 26:45.188
What kind of man
do women from Cangbei like?

26:46.508 --> 26:47.508
Scholarly ones?

26:48.988 --> 26:50.067
Government officials?

26:51.787 --> 26:53.228
Or someone like me,

26:54.107 --> 26:58.107
a genius in business who's charming
and steeped in knowledge across ages?

27:03.587 --> 27:07.627
If only I had learned some martial arts.

27:09.188 --> 27:10.307
What are you doing?

27:10.347 --> 27:11.147
Going home.

27:12.948 --> 27:14.908
Aren't you going to offer some advice?

27:15.188 --> 27:17.107
If you like her,
tell her clearly early on.

27:18.347 --> 27:19.147
I...

27:31.587 --> 27:33.748
Thank you, Master Zhong,
for arriving punctually.

27:35.268 --> 27:39.908
I've been calculating a celestial event
involving a solar eclipse.

27:40.867 --> 27:43.268
I've calculated it should happen
within these few days.

27:43.547 --> 27:48.147
Could you help calculate the exact time
and visibility range over the capital?

27:50.708 --> 27:52.988
I've also done calculations before.

27:54.067 --> 27:57.347
The timing of a solar eclipse
is determined by the lunar phases.

28:00.188 --> 28:03.867
It's tomorrow at noon. Your Highness's
estimation is mostly correct.

28:04.547 --> 28:08.708
However, to precisely determine
the time, direction, and extent

28:09.867 --> 28:11.387
requires further calculation.

28:13.307 --> 28:15.107
Here, take a look.

28:15.107 --> 28:16.268
(Sun and Moon Paths Meet)

28:16.268 --> 28:18.508
This is the moon's path.

28:18.908 --> 28:20.547
And this is the sun's path.

28:22.147 --> 28:24.028
(Sun and Moon Paths Meet)
Where these two paths cross...

28:36.908 --> 28:37.988
Ask her out.

28:39.268 --> 28:42.107
The chrysanthemums
outside the city are in full bloom.

28:46.147 --> 28:48.547
Or, you could go to the temple fair
at the East Market.

28:49.428 --> 28:51.787
I've heard some Hu merchants
have come to the East Market.

28:51.908 --> 28:54.908
Their pastries and sweets
are unlike any in the capital.

28:55.988 --> 28:57.748
What exactly are you trying to do?

28:59.908 --> 29:01.067
Didn't I say it already?

29:01.988 --> 29:03.748
I've been waiting for the right moment.

29:05.268 --> 29:10.107
The timing is upon us now. But how
to get the Dowager Consort to come out?

29:11.908 --> 29:13.067
That's beyond me.

29:13.668 --> 29:15.908
Do you happen to know
her recent whereabouts?

29:17.347 --> 29:18.307
I don't know.

29:18.748 --> 29:19.867
- You can find out.
- You...

29:21.228 --> 29:23.387
This is the Dowager Consort's
Xiankun Miscellany.

29:23.387 --> 29:25.228
It's for the Empress Dowager tomorrow.

29:27.067 --> 29:29.508
Return it to the Dowager Consort
tomorrow at noon.

29:32.784 --> 29:36.336
(Shende Shop)

30:27.067 --> 30:29.668
Where is Wei Zhuang?
Why is he nowhere to be seen?

30:31.428 --> 30:33.627
He... he went to gather new stock.

30:34.028 --> 30:37.268
Business is slow today.
He left me alone to mind the shop.

30:41.268 --> 30:46.307
Ye Li, don't you think the shop
feels different today?

30:49.228 --> 30:50.028
No.

30:50.748 --> 30:53.268
Well, what exactly
are you trying to say?

30:54.668 --> 30:57.627
I tidied up the shop
from top to bottom this morning.

30:58.067 --> 30:59.867
And I've counted all the inventory.

31:00.107 --> 31:03.307
Are... are you sure nothing has changed?

31:12.188 --> 31:13.228
Have you eaten?

31:13.228 --> 31:16.668
I've just finished and haven't eaten.
Let's have a meal together.

31:18.508 --> 31:21.107
If you're too tired to go out,
I'll bring food back for you.

31:21.668 --> 31:23.827
I know a great flatbread shop.

31:25.188 --> 31:26.268
Go eat by yourself.

31:26.948 --> 31:29.268
Your Highness,
let's ignore him and go back.

31:37.827 --> 31:38.627
Feibai?

31:46.387 --> 31:47.228
Don't peek.

31:48.547 --> 31:50.908
Just leave.
What's so appealing about it?

31:56.988 --> 31:59.587
What did you go and do
to get injured this severely?

32:00.347 --> 32:01.428
What happened?

32:04.428 --> 32:05.508
Say something.

32:08.708 --> 32:09.428
It's nothing.

32:10.387 --> 32:14.908
I ran into some bandits
on the way and got into a fight.

32:15.268 --> 32:16.948
I got scraped from the cliff fall.

32:16.948 --> 32:18.347
That was too careless.

32:21.827 --> 32:23.908
By the way, did you find Master Zhu?

32:29.787 --> 32:32.827
Yes, he has returned to the mountain.

32:34.307 --> 32:35.107
Really?

32:36.787 --> 32:39.627
Good that he's back. That's good.

32:41.988 --> 32:42.787
Li,

32:45.147 --> 32:48.268
what do you plan to do
after Lishan Mountain reopens?

32:51.307 --> 32:52.428
What else can I do?

32:53.268 --> 32:56.268
To be with Mo Xiuyao and live well.

32:57.827 --> 32:59.028
Do you love him?

33:00.307 --> 33:02.627
Of course, he is my husband.

33:04.468 --> 33:06.107
Your wish will surely come true.

33:09.748 --> 33:13.508
Alright, go back and rest.
Get some good sleep.

33:19.188 --> 33:19.988
Li,

33:21.387 --> 33:22.827
no matter what happens,

33:23.708 --> 33:24.748
always remember

33:25.040 --> 33:29.067
you still have me,
and I'll always stay by your side.

33:29.552 --> 33:31.827
So you'll never be alone again.

33:35.228 --> 33:38.268
Why say this suddenly?

33:41.107 --> 33:44.067
Nothing. I just hope you stay well.

33:45.627 --> 33:46.508
I will.

34:00.107 --> 34:01.787
Your Highness, I'll get the carriage.

34:10.308 --> 34:11.627
He's not that formidable.

34:14.067 --> 34:17.227
I clashed with him before,
a brawler with no proper training.

34:17.747 --> 34:21.067
He even took advantage of my injury
and struck from behind.

34:22.508 --> 34:24.828
Now if we fought head-on,

34:26.348 --> 34:27.508
I might not lose to him.

34:29.067 --> 34:31.788
Then go find him and have a fight.

34:37.988 --> 34:39.267
I can beat him.

34:44.147 --> 34:45.508
But I can't beat you.

34:56.147 --> 34:57.707
What's that man to you?

34:58.147 --> 35:01.587
Aren't you married?
Should you be alone with him?

35:02.948 --> 35:06.067
Aren't you afraid
your husband will find out?

35:07.948 --> 35:10.667
Exactly. My husband
is incredibly impressive.

35:11.267 --> 35:14.107
If you keep loitering here,
I'll tell him.

35:14.627 --> 35:17.627
I'm not leaving. I like working here.

35:20.587 --> 35:22.187
Your Highness, the carriage is here.

35:23.948 --> 35:24.788
As you wish.

35:26.308 --> 35:27.107
Let's go.

35:56.227 --> 35:57.147
Something on your mind?

35:58.267 --> 36:00.627
Yao, let's make a bet.

36:01.468 --> 36:02.227
Bet on what?

36:02.828 --> 36:06.587
I bet the sun will disappear
at the start of the noon hour tomorrow.

36:38.267 --> 36:41.348
I heard Your Highness arrived.
Why didn't you announce yourself?

36:43.388 --> 36:46.468
Why the lantern in broad daylight?

36:47.547 --> 36:51.348
And you? Why all the flashy clothes
in your own shop?

36:53.388 --> 36:55.267
Well? How do I look?

36:56.227 --> 36:57.428
The hat isn't great.

36:58.028 --> 36:59.227
I just got it.

37:00.747 --> 37:02.028
Perhaps it's the outfit's fault.

37:02.428 --> 37:04.747
Let me change
and you can give me advice.

37:23.067 --> 37:23.908
They're here.

37:29.627 --> 37:30.627
Such strong wind!

37:30.627 --> 37:31.988
Why the sudden wind?

37:33.187 --> 37:34.388
A celestial anomaly!

37:34.707 --> 37:35.908
It's a celestial anomaly!

37:36.428 --> 37:37.627
Is a downpour coming?

37:39.707 --> 37:40.788
Hurry back!

37:40.788 --> 37:41.547
Pack up the stall!

37:41.547 --> 37:42.868
Something's wrong.

37:57.107 --> 37:57.667
Look!

37:57.667 --> 37:58.428
What is that?

37:59.147 --> 38:00.308
Mother, look!

38:00.308 --> 38:01.908
The sun is being eaten!

38:24.067 --> 38:24.908
Go home now!

38:27.747 --> 38:28.828
Watch where you're going!

38:29.627 --> 38:30.896
The Heavenly Dog eats the sun!

38:30.988 --> 38:32.028
Run!

38:33.147 --> 38:33.828
Wrap up quick!

38:41.868 --> 38:42.627
Watch out!

39:42.147 --> 39:43.988
Dowager Consort, are you alright?

39:54.227 --> 39:57.747
Empress Dowager, we don't know
what this celestial phenomena...

40:01.308 --> 40:03.788
What? It's getting bright again?

40:10.800 --> 40:11.828
(Ren'an Clinic)

40:11.828 --> 40:12.627
Let me.

40:20.468 --> 40:23.667
No need to worry, Dowager Consort.
I know some medicine.

40:23.948 --> 40:25.747
I'll treat the wound properly.

40:32.227 --> 40:35.348
Princess Ding,
why were you there just now?

40:36.428 --> 40:39.667
I own a shop
dealing in antiques and paintings.

40:39.868 --> 40:40.948
It's not far from there.

40:42.868 --> 40:45.747
An art dealer lighting a lantern
in broad daylight?

40:47.028 --> 40:48.067
It was only a coincidence.

40:50.747 --> 40:53.348
What a coincidence,
this once-in-a-century sky.

40:53.908 --> 40:56.508
What a coincidence
that we were both on the street.

40:56.788 --> 40:59.828
What a coincidence
that you were also holding a lantern.

41:00.547 --> 41:02.747
How could there be so many coincidences?

41:04.107 --> 41:05.547
There are even bigger coincidences.

41:06.508 --> 41:10.107
Lishan Academy compiled
historical records spanning millennia.

41:10.948 --> 41:12.667
If you read them, you'd know

41:13.348 --> 41:15.107
that given a long enough time span,

41:15.707 --> 41:18.667
the strangest coincidences
become possible.

41:22.908 --> 41:24.828
Dowager Consort, it's done.

41:26.948 --> 41:28.067
Thank you, Princess Ding.

41:29.648 --> 41:32.308
(Ren'an Clinic)

41:32.308 --> 41:33.348
Safe journey.

41:50.224 --> 41:53.908
(Office)

41:53.908 --> 41:55.348
Get the carriage. We'll go back.

41:55.547 --> 41:56.348
Yes.

42:44.816 --> 42:47.920
(Preview)

42:48.187 --> 42:51.948
In fact, I too have a slight grasp
of Master Xiankun's technique

42:52.028 --> 42:53.667
of stirring the elements with his brush

42:53.988 --> 42:55.568
and painting a dragon to summon rain.

42:55.948 --> 42:58.988
Good, I would like to see
if that technique from the past

42:59.348 --> 43:01.028
can still be recreated today.

43:01.388 --> 43:05.147
If he learns the truth about the edict,
what will he think of you?

43:05.547 --> 43:07.348
He is my enemy!

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
